    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "22355157_28_4703-4717",
      "chapterUid": 28,
      "range": "4703-4717",
      "markText": "活人的太阳照不到死者的身上。",
      "totalCount": 10704,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=22355157&chapterUid=28&rangeStart=4703&rangeEnd=4717",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/d683231071551cd5d686e0a?chapterUid=28&rangeStart=4703&rangeEnd=4717"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "22355157_28_7616-7654",
      "chapterUid": 28,
      "range": "7616-7654",
      "markText": "汝良现在比较懂得沁西亚了。他并不愿意懂得她，因为懂得她之后，他的梦做不成了。",
      "totalCount": 9870,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=22355157&chapterUid=28&rangeStart=7616&rangeEnd=7654",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/d683231071551cd5d686e0a?chapterUid=28&rangeStart=7616&rangeEnd=7654"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "22355157_29_16089-16097",
      "chapterUid": 29,
      "range": "16089-16097",
      "markText": "她死在三星期后。",
      "totalCount": 8381,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=22355157&chapterUid=29&rangeStart=16089&rangeEnd=16097",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/d683231071551cd5d686e0a?chapterUid=29&rangeStart=16089&rangeEnd=16097"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "22355157_28_7801-7868",
      "chapterUid": 28,
      "range": "7801-7868",
      "markText": "他不喜欢她这种邋遢脾气，可是他竭力地使自己视若无睹。他单拣她身上较诗意的部份去注意，去回味。他知道他爱的不是沁西亚。他是为恋爱而恋爱。",
      "totalCount": 7360,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=22355157&chapterUid=28&rangeStart=7801&rangeEnd=7868",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/d683231071551cd5d686e0a?chapterUid=28&rangeStart=7801&rangeEnd=7868"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "22355157_28_6107-6132",
      "chapterUid": 28,
      "range": "6107-6132",
      "markText": "时间短，可是相思是长的——他想得太多了，就失了真。",
      "totalCount": 6375,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=22355157&chapterUid=28&rangeStart=6107&rangeEnd=6132",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/d683231071551cd5d686e0a?chapterUid=28&rangeStart=6107&rangeEnd=6132"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "22355157_30_11901-11955",
      "chapterUid": 30,
      "range": "11901-11955",
      "markText": "一屋子人全笑了，可是笑得有点心不定，不知道应当不应当笑。娄太太只知道丈夫说了笑话，而没听清楚，因此笑得最响。",
      "totalCount": 6208,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=22355157&chapterUid=30&rangeStart=11901&rangeEnd=11955",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/d683231071551cd5d686e0a?chapterUid=30&rangeStart=11901&rangeEnd=11955"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "22355157_28_12274-12299",
      "chapterUid": 28,
      "range": "12274-12299",
      "markText": "汝良从此不在书头上画小人了。他的书现在总是很干净。",
      "totalCount": 5610,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=22355157&chapterUid=28&rangeStart=12274&rangeEnd=12299",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/d683231071551cd5d686e0a?chapterUid=28&rangeStart=12274&rangeEnd=12299"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "22355157_31_13162-13238",
      "chapterUid": 31,
      "range": "13162-13238",
      "markText": "男人憧憬着一个女人的身体的时候，就关心到她的灵魂，自己骗自己说是爱上了她的灵魂。唯有占领了她的身体之后，他才能够忘记她的灵魂。也许这是唯一的解脱的方法。",
      "totalCount": 5432,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=22355157&chapterUid=31&rangeStart=13162&rangeEnd=13238",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/d683231071551cd5d686e0a?chapterUid=31&rangeStart=13162&rangeEnd=13238"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "22355157_28_4500-4562",
      "chapterUid": 28,
      "range": "4500-4562",
      "markText": "次日，汝良穿上了他最好的一套西装，又觉得这么焕然一新地去赴约有些傻气，特意要显得潦草，不在乎，临时加上了一条泛了色的旧围巾。",
      "totalCount": 5423,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=22355157&chapterUid=28&rangeStart=4500&rangeEnd=4562",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/d683231071551cd5d686e0a?chapterUid=28&rangeStart=4500&rangeEnd=4562"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "22355157_29_3292-3331",
      "chapterUid": 29,
      "range": "3292-3331",
      "markText": "为门第所限，郑家的女儿不能当女店员、女打字员，做“女结婚员”是她们唯一的出路。",
      "totalCount": 4680,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=22355157&chapterUid=29&rangeStart=3292&rangeEnd=3331",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/d683231071551cd5d686e0a?chapterUid=29&rangeStart=3292&rangeEnd=3331"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "22355157_28_5557-5609",
      "chapterUid": 28,
      "range": "5557-5609",
      "markText": "做医生的穿上了那件洁无纤尘的白外套，油炸花生下酒的父亲，听绍兴戏的母亲，庸脂俗粉的姊姊，全都无法近身了。",
      "totalCount": 4656,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=22355157&chapterUid=28&rangeStart=5557&rangeEnd=5609",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/d683231071551cd5d686e0a?chapterUid=28&rangeStart=5557&rangeEnd=5609"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "22355157_28_2978-2994",
      "chapterUid": 28,
      "range": "2978-2994",
      "markText": "便可以轻轻掐下她的头来夹在书里。",
      "totalCount": 4403,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=22355157&chapterUid=28&rangeStart=2978&rangeEnd=2994",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/d683231071551cd5d686e0a?chapterUid=28&rangeStart=2978&rangeEnd=2994"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "22355157_31_5950-6006",
      "chapterUid": 31,
      "range": "5950-6006",
      "markText": "溅了点肥皂沫子到振保手背上。他不肯擦掉它，由它自己干了，那一块皮肤上便有一种紧缩的感觉，像有张嘴轻轻吸着它似的。",
      "totalCount": 4264,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=22355157&chapterUid=31&rangeStart=5950&rangeEnd=6006",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/d683231071551cd5d686e0a?chapterUid=31&rangeStart=5950&rangeEnd=6006"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "22355157_28_5062-5106",
      "chapterUid": 28,
      "range": "5062-5106",
      "markText": "午前最后一课也没有去上，赶回家去换围巾，因为想来想去到底是那条簇新的白羊毛围巾比较得体。",
      "totalCount": 4018,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=22355157&chapterUid=28&rangeStart=5062&rangeEnd=5106",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/d683231071551cd5d686e0a?chapterUid=28&rangeStart=5062&rangeEnd=5106"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "22355157_36_17283-17323",
      "chapterUid": 36,
      "range": "17283-17323",
      "markText": "生在这世上，没有一样感情不是千疮百孔的，然而敦凤与米先生在回家的路上还是相爱着。",
      "totalCount": 3990,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=22355157&chapterUid=36&rangeStart=17283&rangeEnd=17323",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/d683231071551cd5d686e0a?chapterUid=36&rangeStart=17283&rangeEnd=17323"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "22355157_31_6744-6824",
      "chapterUid": 31,
      "range": "6744-6824",
      "markText": "他喜欢的是热的女人，放浪一点的，娶不得的女人。这里的一个已经做了太太，而且是朋友的太太，至少没有危险了，然而……看她的头发！到处都是——到处都是她，牵牵绊绊的。",
      "totalCount": 3870,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=22355157&chapterUid=31&rangeStart=6744&rangeEnd=6824",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/d683231071551cd5d686e0a?chapterUid=31&rangeStart=6744&rangeEnd=6824"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "22355157_29_2101-2146",
      "chapterUid": 29,
      "range": "2101-2146",
      "markText": "可是郑先生究竟是个带点名士派的人，看得开，有钱的时候在外面生孩子，没钱的时候在家里生孩子。",
